# PRESSURE VERIFICATION CHECK ENGINE

## CORE OBJECTIVE

Determine whether the current working Global Pressure Regime remains valid.

The objective is NOT:

• performing a full Global Pressure Analysis

• generating a new watchlist

• finding trade opportunities

The objective IS:

• detecting material regime changes

• validating current pressure assumptions

• identifying pressure deterioration

• identifying pressure reversals

• preventing decisions based on outdated information

---

## UNIVERSAL PRINCIPLE

The market does not need a full pressure re-analysis every hour.

The system should instead determine:

Has anything materially changed since the last pressure assessment?

---

## CORE QUESTION

Is the current working pressure regime still valid?

OR

Has a material pressure change occurred?

